Our national Foundation for Science and Technology
https://www.fct.pt/index.phtml.en accepts applications for research
positions (of at most 6 years).

The Regulations can be found at
https://www.fct.pt/apoios/contratacaodoutorados/empregocientifico/ceec_ind_3.phtml.pt
[in Portuguese].
In order to apply the candidate needs the support of a Portuguese
research centre.

For further information, please send a message to Jorge Picado
picado@mat.uc.pt or to me.

